# Reference

This directory indexes supporting reference material for `<repo-name>`.

## Belongs Here

- supporting examples and reference notes
- implementation-facing documentation notes
- lookup material that supports the repository documentation model

## Does Not Belong Here

- current canonical guidance: `../Architecture/`
- open design alternatives: `../Proposals/`
- decision records and rationale: `../Decisions/`
- migration rollout records: `../Migrations/`

## Use

Use this subtree for supporting material that helps readers apply the
documentation structure without defining current truth.
